Privacy Policy – Karmalak


Karmalak we respects your privacy and is committed to protecting the personal information of our users. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information when you use our coupons app.

1. Information We Collect

Personal Information: We may collect basic information such as your name, email address, or phone number if you choose to register or contact us.

Non-Personal Information: We may collect non-identifiable information such as device type, app usage statistics, and general location (city/region) to improve our services.

2. How We Use Information

We use collected information only for:

Providing access to coupons, discounts, and promotions.

Improving app functionality and user experience.

Sending notifications about new coupons or offers (if you enable notifications).

3. Data Sharing

We do not sell, trade, or rent users’ personal information to third parties.
We may share limited non-personal information with trusted service providers for analytics and app improvement purposes.

4. Data Security

We implement reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse. However, no method of electronic storage is 100% secure.

5. User Choices

You can disable notifications at any time in your device settings.

You may request deletion of your account or personal information by contacting us at: [Insert Contact Email].

6. Third-Party Links

The app may contain links to third-party websites or offers. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external services.

7. Children’s Privacy

Karmalak is not intended for children under the age of 13, and we do not knowingly collect data from them.
